steps.name: I am on SFWF Front Office Home Page GOC "Chrome"
I Input Registered Maupass User's Username "ybhunjun5" and Password "Mauritius1!1710"
I Click on Sign In button in Maupass
I Verify Applicant's Successful Login
I Click on Register as Farmer
I Verify that User is directed to My Application Page
I Verify display of Farmers Card link
I Verify Programmes link
I Click on Programmes
I Click on New Programmes
I Verify Programme Type Page
I Click to Apply for Group Personal Accident Cover (GPAC)
I Verify Display of INDIAN OCEAN GENERAL ASSURANCE (IOGA) / SMALL FARMERS WELFARE FUND (SFWF)
I Input Type of Farmer "Small Planter"
I Input Accident Particulars "01/10/2024" "11:45 AM" "Karo Cane" "Explosion" "Planting Cane" "Engine exploded"
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify General Information Tab
I Input Medical Cost "45000"
I Select "Yes" for Has the medical treatment related to the accident been completed?
I Select "Yes" for If yes, are there any additional medical charges?
I Input "Surgery abroad" for Details of Additional Medical Charges
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Upload Required Documents Page is displayed
I Click on Add Additional Document
I Input Additional Document Name "Add Doc Test"
I Verify Success message for adding Additional Document Name
I Upload Documents "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Verify for Document Upload Success Message
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Terms and Conditions Page
I click on I agree to the Terms and Conditions
I Click on Submit Application "Yes"
I Verify Success message for Application of Programmes Submitted
I Copy Programmes Ref Number
I Sign Out as Front Registered User
I am on SFWF Back Office Home Page GOC "Chrome"
I Input WPO Username "WPO" and Password "Admin@123"
I Click on Sign In button
I Verify Successful Login
I Click to view All Programmes
I Search for Programmes Ref Number as a Back Office User
I Click to view Programmes
I Click on Action Button
I Select Under Query for Programmes
I Input External Remarks "This is a Test"
I Click on Under Query Notification for Programmes
I Verify Success Message for Under Query Notification for Programmes
I Click on Save Actions for Programmes
I Verify for success message for workflow saved
I Sign Out
I Verify Successful Sign Out
